target: ui
agent_profile: null
validations:
  - name: ui_completeness
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify the UI implementation includes:
        1. A title screen with the game name, a star character, drifting shape background, and a "press any key" prompt.
        2. An in-game HUD displaying: 60-second countdown timer (with color change as time runs low), lives as star icons, health pips, current level indicator, and dash cooldown.
        3. A pause menu (Escape key) that freezes the game and offers Resume, Restart Level, and Quit to Title options.
        4. A game over screen showing level reached and time survived, with Retry and Quit to Title options.
        5. A victory screen with a celebratory particle animation of all three shape types and total time display.
        6. All UI rendered on Canvas (no HTML overlays or DOM elements for game UI).
